Download [[Signing Key|{{project_name_long}} Signing Key]]. <ref>
See [[Secure_Downloads|Secure Downloads]] to understand why <code>curl</code> and the parameters <code>--tlsv1.3 --proto =https</code> are used instead of <code>wget</code>.
</ref>

{{Box|text=
<u>'''If''' you are using Debian</u>, run.

{{CodeSelect|code=
curl --tlsv1.3 --proto =https --max-time 180 --output ~/derivative.asc https://www.{{project_clearnet}}/derivative.asc
}}

<u>'''If''' you are using a Qubes Debian Template</u>, run.

{{CodeSelect|code=
curl --proxy http://127.0.0.1:8082/ --tlsv1.3 --proto =https --max-time 180 --output ~/derivative.asc https://www.{{project_clearnet}}/derivative.asc
}}
}}

Users can [[Signing Key|<u>check</u> {{project_name_long}} Signing Key]] for better security.

Add {{project_name_long}} signing key to APT trusted keys.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo cp ~/derivative.asc /usr/share/keyrings/derivative.asc
}}

The procedure of adding {{project_name_long}} signing key is now complete.
